reviewText: this is a awesome movie. this is a great story for Aquaman. it's about time they did his movie. even though it is titled justice league it's Aquaman's film. this movie is great. the animation is great and the voice talents are awesome. the action is great too. this is just another great dc universe animated film. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do P.S. they should do martian manhunter next
